Internship Infobip Virtual Classroom

Learned about the latest technologies in software engineering, presales engineering and core operations. Created chatbot, own solutions and got badges for participating the classes. Startup „Better life“ Analyzing persons needs to be more successful in life through modules health, career, school, finance, be happy, etc. Mobile application in React Native + Node.js, investment process using Blockchain technology. Bachelor thesis - Machine learning project Analyzed a dataset of travel reviews and deciding which place is the best in “East Asia” according to reviews using machine learning techniques, ML database and Python programming language. Web application “Reservation process” Worked with HTML, CSS, JavaScript to create a frontend of this application and worked with Node.js, Express.js, Ajax for backend and PhpMyAdmin database for creating tables and queries. Virtual reality application “Colosseum” Designed an antique Colosseum using Blender and worked with Unity to represent it like a virtual reality application. Matlab programs Analyzed problems and resolved them using Matlab on the different courses „Artificial intelligence“ and „Computer modelling“. Webpage „ETFMedia“ using WordPress During the course „Business web systems“ we developed a webpage ETFMedia for a marketing agency using WordPress. Information system „Rent a car agency“ Experience as a leader where I worked with my team on different tasks about the information system "Rent a car agency". Information system for „Red Cross“ Created a module Mines with my team as the information system for “Red Cross”. We analyzed everything about mines competitions and all requirements which they need in a system. Application „Online dashboard for professors“ Developed an online dashboard for professors with my team using React.js, and Node.js. The professors together with assistants can make a schedule about students, their exams and more. Application Auction I was at the position of a full-stack developer at an internship in AtlantBH, where I learned new technologies as Ember.js, Spring Boot and PostgreSQL all of these skills were incorporated in the application Auction. Project “Calculator” using Matlab, MplabX and Microchip16F1939 Created a calculator with my team member using Microchip16F1939, MplabX environment with C programming language and serial communication using Matlab. C and C++ programs, data structures and algorithms Learned object-oriented principles and programming logic using C and C++ programming languages and the advanced programming techniques trough subject „Data structures and algorithms”. Application “Refugees welcome" Designed an application for refugees with my team members where refugees have everything from accommodation, health care, food, education, ability to go outside of the country with just with one-click. Betting house using MySql database Created a database for Betting house using Mysql and all knowledge that we learned at the subject “Database fundamentals”. Worked with triggers, procedures and views and all of these things are incorporated into queries.
